<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.5;
      color: #333;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .header {
      border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
      padding-bottom: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777;
    }
    .error {
      background-color: #fff0f0;
      border-left: 4px solid #dc3545;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .help {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>We Encountered an Error</h1>
    </div>
    
    <p>Hello <%= @email %>,</p>
    
    <p>We were unable to process your request due to the following error:</p>
    
    <div class="error">
      <p><strong>Error:</strong> <%= @error_message %></p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="help">
      <h3>Need assistance?</h3>
      <p>If you're having trouble, here are some common solutions:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Make sure you're using the correct email format and commands</li>
        <li>Check that all required information is included in your email</li>
        <li>For adding addresses, ensure the address is formatted correctly</li>
      </ul>
      <p>You can reply to this email if you need further help.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>© <%= Date.today.year %> PostcardMailer.us</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 